narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yeah absolutely - great skill to pick up.
Spanish 120 is hard, but you learn a lot. Just don't slack off because everything builds on everything that came before it.

I would not recommend this section of the class. While Brais was incredibly nice, we spent all of class doing exercises from the textbook. We had virtually no opportunities to practice having conversations in spanish, and I think my speaking skills got worse over the course of the semester.
